    "eventDescription": "2nd Wednesday of Every Other Month\nSpeaker: Megan Davis Hudson Counseling & Wellness",
    "eventFullDescription": "<p class=\"PSXEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Join the Professional Women’s Network, a community designed to empower and connect women in all industries. This network offers a platform for professional women to share experiences, exchange ideas, and support one another's growth. Whether you're looking to advance your career, build meaningful relationships, or find inspiration, this is the place to thrive and collaborate with like-minded women. Let’s grow stronger together!</span><br><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Professional Women's Network is sponsored by&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.apexskin.com/locations/hudson-oh-dermatology-office/\" target=\"_self\" data-formid=\"null\" data-video-url=\"null\" data-url=\"https://www.apexskin.com/locations/hudson-oh-dermatology-office/\" class=\"PSXEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Apex Skin</span></a></p><p class=\"PSXEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">This event is free for Hudson Area Chamber Members.</span><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Participants purchase their own lunch.</span><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Non-Members are welcome to attend up to two events before investing in membership.&nbsp;</span></p>",
