    "eventName": "The Professional Women's Network",
    "eventDescription": "Where local women come together to connect, collaborate, and inspire one another",
    "eventFullDescription": "<p class=\"PSXEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">The heart of the Professional Women’s Network is community. Whether you're seeking advice, mentorship, or just want to connect with other women who understand the unique challenges and opportunities in the professional world, this is the place to be. We believe in lifting each other up and creating an environment where all women can thrive.</span></p><p class=\"PSXEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><b><strong class=\"PSXEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Why You Should Attend:</strong></b></p><ul class=\"PSXEditorTheme__ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"PSXEditorTheme__listItem\" style=\"\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Build and strengthen your professional network</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"PSXEditorTheme__listItem\" style=\"\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gain valuable insights from guest speakers and peers</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"PSXEditorTheme__listItem\" style=\"\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Share experiences and discuss challenges and successes in a supportive setting</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"PSXEditorTheme__listItem\" style=\"\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Discover new opportunities for collaboration, mentorship, and growth</span></li><li value=\"5\" class=\"PSXEditorTheme__listItem\" style=\"\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Enjoy a delicious lunch while fostering meaningful connections</span></li></ul>",
